# Meet ScreenAssist


```playwright
await fx.say("A pro film room every basketball player can run — tag your own plays, build a college-ready reel, share one link.");
await page.waitForLoadState("networkidle");
await page.waitForSelector("h1.display");
await fx.pause(0.6);
```

```overlay
type: callout
target: "h1.display"
text: "The hero pitch — Get seen, on film you already have."
duration: 3s
```

---

# One CTA, no friction


```playwright
await fx.say("The whole site funnels here — every \"Start now\" button drops you into signup. Free during beta, no credit card.");
await fx.cursorTo("nav.top a[href='/signup']");
await fx.highlight("nav.top a[href='/signup']", 1.5);
await fx.pause(0.8);
```

```overlay
type: callout
target: "nav.top a[href='/signup']"
text: "Free during beta · no credit card"
duration: 2.5s
```

---

# How it works


```playwright
await fx.say("Five steps from your film to your future — self-tag plays, get instant stats, surface patterns, auto-build a reel, share one link.");
await page.locator("#how").scrollIntoViewIfNeeded();
await page.waitForTimeout(400);
await fx.pause(0.5);
await fx.cursorTo("#how h2");
await fx.pause(1.2);
```

```overlay
type: callout
target: "#how h2"
text: "The 5-step workflow"
duration: 2.5s
```

