# Start free


```playwright
await fx.say("Pricing, FAQ, and one button to start. The pro film room every player can run.");
await page.locator("#pricing").scrollIntoViewIfNeeded();
await page.waitForTimeout(400);
await fx.pause(0.4);
await fx.cursorTo("#pricing a.btn-primary");
await fx.highlight("#pricing a.btn-primary", 2);
await fx.pause(1.5);
```

```overlay
type: callout
target: "#pricing a.btn-primary"
